snippet.title: QUUR Trailer
snippet.description:
Violence is not always your best option. Quur is a 3D action adventure game, in which your actions have a direct impact on the environment and the creatures.
You can play Quur for free at https://lucie-viatge.itch.io/quur or through our official website http://typhaine-uro.com/quur/
